{"word":"βίβλος","slug":"βίβλος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>βίβλος, ου, ἡ</el></b> [by-form of <el>βύβλος</el> ‘papyrus, paper’] ‘written account’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> as formal list <b><i>registry</i> <a href='B:570 4:3'>Phil 4:3</a>; <a href='B:730 3:5'>Rv 3:5</a>; <a href='B:730 20:15'>20:15</a>.</b> Prob. also <b><a href='B:470 1:1'>Mt 1:1</a>,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> link to next sense<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> as literary production <b><i>book</i></b> (noted individually or collectively) <b><a href='B:480 12:26'>Mk 12:26</a>; <a href='B:490 3:4'>Lk 3:4</a>; <a href='B:510 1:20'>Ac 1:20</a>; <a href='B:510 7:42'>7:42</a>; <a href='B:510 19:19'>19:19</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:βιβλίον\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:βιβρώσκω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}